      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-21/morgan-stanley-s-slimmon-sees-stocks-soaring-beyond-record-highs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利(Morgan Stanley)的安德鲁·斯利蒙(Andrew Slimmon)表示，即使股市创下历史新高，投资者仍坚守现金，这表明市场有足够的空间扩大涨幅。]]></description>
